description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured Garcelle accidentally spilling some secrets, Kathy's search for a straw, (possible) Taco Bell (unclear), Sutton's question mark, takeout, and more! On The Real Housewives of New York, Ramona attempts to get to the bottom of Sonja's finances, and Lu films her holiday music video.


RHONY: 33:35ish
